  "title": "Dense Smoked Egg Tunisian Shoofly Tagine",
  "description": "A post-workout ovo-vegetarian dish combining the flavors of smoked egg, shiso-leaf, and lacquer-glaze, wrapped in a cedar plank.",
  "cuisine": "Tunisian",
